description.value: Een opsomming van alle door Nederland erkende nationaliteiten met hun codes, omschrijvingen en geldigheidstermijnen. Link naar de bron [https://publicaties.rvig.nl/Landelijke_tabellen/Inleiding_op_de_Landelijke_Tabellen_GBA](https://publicaties.rvig.nl/Landelijke_tabellen/Inleiding_op_de_Landelijke_Tabellen_GBA)
A code that indicates the status of the concept. Values found in this version of the code system are: active, deprecated

The date at which a concept was deprecated. Concepts that are deprecated but not inactive can still be used, but their use is discouraged, and they should be expected to be made inactive in a future release. Property type is dateTime. Note that the status property may also be used to indicate that a concept is deprecated
The date at which the concept was status was last changed. This is calculated based on the highest of 'creation date', 'expiration date', and 'official release date'
True if the concept is not considered active - e.g. not a valid concept any more and not approved for current use. Property type is boolean, default value is false
